msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "I have to wonder, what kind of excuse\r\nwere you planning to give Daidoji?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "As you know, keeping the Yamato Mark II\r\nunder wraps was your job. Your responsibility."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "However, it seems you were\r\nunable to fulfill that duty."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "No matter what you say now,\r\nDaidoji would have no reason to listen to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "I don't know what you're talking about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "I suppose I've never mentioned this before<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "But I've known the secret of\r\nOnomichi this whole time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Whenever I spoke to you,\r\nI merely feigned ignorance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "It was 40 years ago. When I was just a kid,\r\na Yomei officer named Matsunaga came to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "He rattled off every last detail."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "At the time, those with knowledge of the secret\r\nwere being slaughtered one by one."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Matsunaga feared he was next."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "So, he chose to entrust me with the secret.\r\nHe also asked that I beg you to spare his life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Tragically, Matsunaga died that very evening."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "But I must say, you botched your own plan.\r\nYou should have silenced everyone at once."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "I see..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Now then, Daidoji and his sympathizers gave you\r\na great deal to keep their battleship hidden."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Political favors of that magnitude are no light matter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Most would consider that to be governmental collusion."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "What are you getting at?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Over the past 70 years, countless politicians and diplomats\r\nhave involved themselves in your plot with Daidoji."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "If that were to come out, our society's darkest secrets\r\nwould be dragged into the light in rapid succession."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "To prevent that, they want to\r\nensure your eternal silence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "And that, is where I come in.\r\nI am the contractor who can fulfill their desire."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "I only have one more question for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Father... Why did you keep\r\nthe secret of Onomichi hidden even from me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "What did you stand to gain from\r\nleaving your own son in the dark!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "If you had known the truth, you would\r\nhave been doomed to a life of crime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "That is not the path I wanted\r\nmy child to walk in the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "No parent would."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "Interesting. So that's why you chose\r\nto have me inherit Iwami Shipbuilding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Yes. It's a world-class shipbuilding manufacturer.\r\nYou should have been pleased."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "That's nothing more than your own selfish opinion!\r\nWhether or not I'm pleased... is my choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "What else could you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "You know, I waited for so many years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Not just to take over your front, but to be\r\naccepted into your criminal organization as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "I didn't want to use the secret of Onomichi as a crutch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "All I wanted was for you to\r\nrecognize the potential I had!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "I should have realized you had no intention of that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "So I took matters into my own hands."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "I made a fool of the Saio Triad's Lo. Won over Sugai.\r\nTurned the Tojo Clan into mere pawns in my hand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "Those are achievements worthy of\r\nthe next chairman of the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "You have done much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "But because you brought Lo here behind my back,\r\nthe battleship's existence was exposed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "You say that, but remember the oath I\r\nattempted to barter with the Tojo Clan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "The one you asked Kazuma Kiryu to witness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "In truth... You only chose him because\r\nyou knew full well that he would decline."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "It was all part of your plan to rein me in, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "However, had you allowed the oath to proceed,\r\nwe would have gained free rein over Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "In fact, the secret would still be under wraps as well.\r\nLo would have been taken care of long ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "So according to you, I am at fault for allowing\r\nthe Yamato Mark II to become known to the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Exactly. And Daidoji sees it my way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "I must say, it was quite a surprise to see\r\nthat ship surfacing on the horizon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "However, it has given me a perfect opportunity.\r\nThe time is nigh for me to take my rightful role."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Hey. You should try to eat, Nagumo-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "It ain't gonna happen, Kiyo-chan.\r\nI ain't hungry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "What about Moreno, Boss?\r\nY'sure it's okay to be closed today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Actually, let's take tomorrow\r\nn' the next day off, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Junko. I'll take a rice ball."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Last night, a massive battleship surfaced in the Iwami\r\nshipyard, Onomichi, measuring in excess of 300 meters."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "It is thought to be even bigger than\r\nthe previous world record holder, the Yamato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "The management at Iwami Shipbuilding claims they do not\r\nknow when or how this ship could have been constructed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "An internal investigation has been opened."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "When there are any findings to announce, a press\r\nconference has been promised that we will carry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "The company remains in turmoil."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "I just heard from Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "He said Haruka's regained consciousness.\r\nApparently, she can even talk a bit, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "F-Fer real?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "What a relief.\r\nMan, I'm glad t'hear that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "Haruka-chan..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san... That's great news."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Sorry for bringing it up now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "What're y'talkin' about?\r\nY'don't gotta apologize fer that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "I dunno, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "Right now, I ain't really sure\r\nhow I'm s'posed t'be feelin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "I jus' can't get my mind off what the boss\r\nwas sayin' right before he died."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Y'know, that part about how he wished\r\nwe coulda been the ones who killed him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "It's weird, though. Even though he told\r\nme he was the one who murdered my dad..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "...I probly never woulda wanted\r\nt'get revenge on him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "I jus' don't get it. Why can't I bring myself\r\nt'hate him fer killing my dad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "It's mutual, Cap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "I was still in elementary school when my dad died."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "I barely even remember that day at this point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Only thing that comes t'mind when\r\nI think of my dad... is Hirose-san's face."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "We were all alone in the world,\r\nbut the boss came n' took us in."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "I was so happy swearin' my oath t'him. That was the day\r\nI could finally start thinkin' o' him as my dad fer real."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "If one thing's clear to me, it's that the bond\r\nbetween you and your boss was very strong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "At first I'm sure the guilt ate away at him,\r\nso he took you guys in as a way of repenting."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "But... the more time you spent together,\r\nthe more he grew to love you like his own children."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "If that wasn't the case, he would've done as Kurusu\r\nasked. You would have died back at the shipyard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "To me, it looks like you guys helped release\r\nyour boss from the curse that hung over him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "100||||4"
msgid "Cap... Matsunaga-aniki..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "In that case... It's okay fer us t'cry\r\nover losin' our boss, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "I happen to be in the area.\r\nCan you meet, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "Is this... Someya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "Yes. I have something I'd like to tell you.\r\nI'll wait for you at the docks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "Hey, hold on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "So that's the secret of Onomichi...\r\nIt's breathtaking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "You came alone?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "110||||4"
msgid "Yes. That should be plain to see,\r\nFourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "And what do you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "First, please accept my condolences.\r\nI heard of Hirose-san's passing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "It is a difficult time for Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "You may not be aware, but\r\nTakeru Kurusu died last night as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "It was suicide, apparently."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Well... the only one actually saying\r\nit was suicide is Tsuneo Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Wait, so Tsuneo Iwami... killed his own father?\r\nJust what exactly is going on here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Didn't I say I had something to tell you?\r\nCalm down and I'll explain everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "So Tsuneo knew, too.\r\nHe was in on the secret of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "He's known for the past 40 years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "123||||4"
msgid "Beyond that, his silencing of Takeru Kurusu last night\r\nauthorized him to inherit the Yomei Alliance throne."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "It appears we underestimated him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "125||||4"
msgid "Tsuneo Iwami is a yakuza through and through."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "I'd planned to seize control of the Tojo Clan\r\nfrom Sugai while the sixth chairman was gone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "However, if Sugai has Iwami's support,\r\nit won't be as easy as I had expected."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "And why come to me with all this?\r\nWhat's your goal here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "I doubt you'll be able to trust me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "...But quite frankly, I'd rather not see you\r\nmurdered by the likes of Tsuneo and Sugai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "It appears Daidoji has instructed them\r\nto dispose of you, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "You exposed the secret of Onomichi, after all.\r\nDaidoji will never forgive you for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "Being inches away from death's door,\r\nhe has discarded all false pretenses."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "As such, he will be coming for both\r\nyou and the Hirose Family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "What!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "As long as you stay in town, the Yomei Alliance\r\nwill continue sending soldiers to kill you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "Every last yakuza in Hiroshima is here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "I'm fairly convinced even a man like you\r\ncan be overwhelmed, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "Not that I see you actually dying before\r\nsuch weak foes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "I should also make it clear that I'm only here now\r\nbecause Sugai ordered me to kill you myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "To be blunt, Sugai intends to sell\r\nthe entire Tojo Clan to Tsuneo Iwami."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "143||||4"
msgid "And if it bends the knee to Hiroshima,\r\nthe Tojo Clan will wither and die."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Even after the sixth chairman gets out of prison,\r\nSugai won't just hand back the throne."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "He may have grand plans, but he's just\r\nan antique trying to stay relevant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "He's apparently searching for\r\nHaruka Sawamura and her child as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "My advice is that you take both of them and\r\nhide somewhere far away for a long time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "I'll repay you for this someday."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "I'd rather you forget, actually."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "Once I've wrested control of the Tojo from Sugai,\r\nyou and I will need to settle things for good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "And I won't make you wait long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "(If Someya's telling the truth, the Hirose Family\r\nis in danger. I have to go tell them!)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "Hey, look! That's Kiryu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "Go n' get him!\r\nWhoever takes his head's gettin' promoted!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "Fight like yer life depends on it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "You're okay!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "Wh-What's up, Aniki?\r\nY'look like ya jus' saw a ghost."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Where're the girls?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "Well, they jus' left."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "Okay. I assume they're still safe, but\r\nI'll need you to call them just in case."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "For the time being, they should\r\nprobably leave Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "The Yomei Alliance and\r\nthe Tojo Clan are coming for us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "It's because we revealed the secret of Onomichi.\r\nApparently Daidoji's not too pleased with that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "G-Gotcha!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "I'll drop a line over to Moreno."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "Aniki, we got guests. Looks like main family guys.\r\nOnly a handful of 'em, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "Didn't these shits learn their lesson at the shipyard?\r\nI'm gettin' real tired of bein' underestimated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "No, this is just the scouting party."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "Every yakuza in Hiroshima is coming for us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "We told the ladies where t'go.\r\nThey'll be safe fer now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "If we stick together, we can win this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "These fools... Let's make them regret\r\never setting their sights on our family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "Aniki, did... Did y'just say \"our\" family?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "I don't know about you,\r\nbut that's how I've felt since I got here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "All right, let's crush 'em!\r\nThis one's fer Patriarch Hirose!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "These fuckin' fuckheads..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "Keep an eye outside for me.\r\nI need to get in touch with Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "Why Yuta?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "The Tojo Clan is coming for Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "They mean business, too. I doubt\r\nthe police hospital will be safe anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "Tagashira. More o' those main family guys'll\r\nprobly swing by. Keep an eye on the streets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "Aniki? It's Yuta."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "Right. How is everything over there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "It's going pretty good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah, Haruto stood up today without\r\nany help from either of us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "He may even walk soon!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "Great.\r\nIs Date-san with you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "I need you to tell him something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "He needs to move Haruka\r\nsomewhere safe, as soon as possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "Far away from Kamurocho, if he can.\r\nMaybe even outside of Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "But what kinda place would be\r\nsafer than a police hospital?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "On top o' that, Haruka-chan just woke up.\r\nShe's still not in the greatest shape."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "It'd be tough to move her right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "That makes sense. Okay then,\r\nI'll head back as soon as I can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "But tell Date-san to start searching\r\nfor a safer hideout. This is important."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "Will do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "You heard all that, right? I'm bound for Kamurocho.\r\nNagumo, what's your plan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "We're goin' with.\r\nWe gotta protect Haruka-chan n' her baby."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "That's how the boss woulda wanted it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "Okay then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "We still gotta prep a bit, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "If I had to guess, it'll be real tough\r\nto come back this way now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "Don't leave anythin' undone\r\nbefore we roll out, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "We'll drop by yer apartment later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "(The Hirose guys are meeting me here.\r\nAm I ready to leave Onomichi behind?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "(All right, I'm ready.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "(I just have to wait for them now.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "210||||4"
msgid "(I still have things to do.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "(I should walk the town a little more.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "I'll be damned...\r\nThis is Kamurocho, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "213||||4"
msgid "Wow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "Y'can't light up here, Tagashira.\r\nThem's the rules."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "This place ain't like back home.\r\nY'gotta mind yer manners. Ain't that right, Aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "Take these two over to Serena, Nagumo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "I'm going to catch a taxi to the police hospital."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "The heck, Kiryu-aniki? Y'mean we came\r\nt'Tokyo jus' to sit on our asses?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "Don't backtalk him, Tagashira."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "220||||4"
msgid "This shit's important fer Kiryu-aniki. He hasn't\r\ntalked t'Haruka-chan in years. Respect up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "Thanks for that, Nagumo. I appreciate it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "S'all good. N' don't worry 'bout comin'\r\nback late. Take yer sweet time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "Akiyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "Welcome back, Kiryu-san.\r\nGlad to see you're safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "Date-san and I are on the hunt for somewhere\r\nto stash Haruka-chan. Sounded urgent."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "Did you manage to find anything?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "More or less."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "Remember we're going up against\r\nthe Yomei Alliance and Tojo Clan here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "They can never, ever find Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "I get it. Then staying in one place\r\nis probably out of the picture, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "She might have to move around a bit\r\nto keep them off her trail."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "233||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "234||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "235||||4"
msgid "Am I... putting you in danger again?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236||||4"
msgid "No, that's not it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "So much happened while you were asleep.\r\nThey're coming for me this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "It's my fault. You wouldn't be in danger if not for me.\r\nStill... I'm going to do something about it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "You, Haruto, and even Yuta...\r\nI need to make sure you can live together in peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240||||4"
msgid "Huh? Uh, well, only if Haruka-chan's\r\ninto the idea, of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "Yuta-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "242||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "Why wouldn't I be into the idea?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "Are y'sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san. I think you and I are\r\nthe third and fourth wheels here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "Wait, you're actually leaving?\r\nI was kidding, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "Hold on, Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "249||||4"
msgid "It's fine.\r\nI have a call to make."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "A call? Who to?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "251||||4"
msgid "Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu.\r\nSomeya. Can you talk?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "253||||4"
msgid "I can. How are you, Fourth Chairman?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "254||||4"
msgid "I didn't call to make small talk.\r\nJust tell me where Iwami and Sugai are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "255||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately, I'm not sure of Iwami's whereabouts.\r\nSugai is over in the Millennium Tower, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "256||||4"
msgid "His office is up on the top floor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "I see. Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "Hold on. What are you planning?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "Are you going to see Sugai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "261||||4"
msgid "You won't be able to talk your way out of this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "262||||4"
msgid "As you know, Tsuneo plans on delivering your head\r\nto Daidoji as proof of his commitment to their cause."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "263||||4"
msgid "From his standpoint,\r\nnegotiations are off the table."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "I'd advise that you stay off his radar\r\nuntil Daidoji takes his last gasp."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "It couldn't be much longer now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "266||||4"
msgid "If I were the only one this affected,\r\nmaybe I would."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "267||||4"
msgid "But I'm not. I can't run if it means\r\nabandoning everyone close to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "268||||4"
msgid "So then..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "270||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman... You can't be serious.\r\nAre you... planning to kill Sugai and Tsuneo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "271||||4"
msgid "I'm shocked. I never thought the day would come\r\nthat the Dragon of Dojima killed a man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "272||||4"
msgid "I heard that's against your policy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "273||||4"
msgid "I never said I was a saint."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "274||||4"
msgid "In that case, a word of caution."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "275||||4"
msgid "Sugai has escape routes throughout\r\nthe Millennium Tower."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276||||4"
msgid "Even if you managed to reach his office, you would\r\nnever be able to block off all of them by yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "277||||4"
msgid "He could sneak away with ease."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "278||||4"
msgid "That so? I got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "279||||4"
msgid "Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280||||4"
msgid "Yuta. I'll be needing your help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "281||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "282||||4"
msgid "We're going to the Millennium Tower to take Sugai down.\r\nYou should go meet up with the others at Serena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "283||||4"
msgid "R-Right, I'm on it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284||||4"
msgid "Can you look after Haruka for me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "285||||4"
msgid "I think not, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "286||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "287||||4"
msgid "The Dragon of Dojima's back in Kamurocho busting heads\r\nlike the good old days, and you want me to babysit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288||||4"
msgid "If you want someone to look after Haruka-chan,\r\nDate-san and the police have it covered."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "289||||4"
msgid "After all, you can't take the police on this one.\r\nBut you can take me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "290||||4"
msgid "The Hirose Family and I... We already have Sugai\r\ncoming after us. You shouldn't get involved."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "291||||4"
msgid "Don't gimme the short straw, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "292||||4"
msgid "Besides, I had to sit and watch Kamurocho\r\ngo to hell after Sugai took over as chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "293||||4"
msgid "I couldn't stop him, though. All I did was\r\nsit on my garbage throne in the sewers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "294||||4"
msgid "This is my chance to get back at Sugai.\r\nConsider me the Kamurocho representative."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "295||||4"
msgid "And I'm not letting this opportunity pass."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296||||4"
msgid "Akiyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "297||||4"
msgid "I'm going with you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "298||||4"
msgid "And don't even try to pretend\r\nlike you don't need me there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "299||||4"
msgid "I'd rather have you than a hundred other guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300||||4"
msgid "I'll be waiting over at Serena, too. If you don't\r\ncome soon, it'll be you who gets left behind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "301||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "302||||4"
msgid "I'm going to borrow Yuta for a bit.\r\nI need his help with something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "303||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "304||||4"
msgid "I'll bring him back safe.\r\nI promise you that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "305||||4"
msgid "But... what about you, Uncle Kaz?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "306||||4"
msgid "I'll be fine, too. Of course."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "307||||4"
msgid "Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308||||4"
msgid "You have a good kid here.\r\nHe looks like his mother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "310||||4"
msgid "I always wondered when this day would come.\r\nIt was just way sooner than I expected."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "311||||4"
msgid "If you take the \"Haruka\" kanji from my name,\r\nand combine it with the \"Yu\" kanji from Yuta's..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "312||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "313||||4"
msgid "It reads like \"Haruto.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "314||||4"
msgid "Ah, the \"to\" was Yuta's name..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "315||||4"
msgid "Um... Yuta-kun is a good guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "316||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I know... I know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "317||||4"
msgid "Are you sure? He told me you punched\r\nhim straight through a door."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "318||||4"
msgid "Hm? Oh, uh... That was, uh...\r\nHow do I explain...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "319||||4"
msgid "Uncle Kaz."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "320||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "321||||4"
msgid "Come back in one piece, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "322||||4"
msgid "You're a great mother already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "323||||4"
msgid "I guess I can't keep patting\r\nyou on the head after this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "325||||4"
msgid "But for now, I'm going to make\r\nsure you stay out of this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "326||||4"
msgid "I'd never forgive myself if I couldn't."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "327||||4"
msgid "I'll see you later, Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "329||||4"
msgid "(Everyone is waiting for me at Serena.\r\nI should go meet up with them.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "330||||4"
msgid "(We're about to break into the Millennium Tower.\r\nI better go into it with no regrets.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "331||||4"
msgid "(Okay, I'm ready to go.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "332||||4"
msgid "(Let's take Sugai down.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "333||||4"
msgid "(I still have some things to do.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "334||||4"
msgid "(I should come back once I'm ready.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "335||||4"
msgid "Yuta told us everythin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "336||||4"
msgid "We're takin' down Sugai from the Tojo Clan, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "337||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I need to talk to him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "338||||4"
msgid "But before I do, I'll need your help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "339||||4"
msgid "I can't wait t'show Kamurocho what's up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "340||||4"
msgid "We're gonna give these Tokyo shits a taste\r\no' how we do it down in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "341||||4"
msgid "This kinda stuff's perfect fer yakuza like us.\r\nI jus' wish Hirose-san coulda seen it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "343||||4"
msgid "Let's do it, Aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "344||||4"
msgid "Our destination is the Millennium Tower.\r\nSugai should be on the top floor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "345||||4"
msgid "Catch him, no matter what.\r\nWe can't let him escape. Understand?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "346||||4"
msgid "Let's head up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "347||||4"
msgid "Shit, they just don't stop!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "348||||4"
msgid "We'll stay back n' take care of 'em.\r\nYou guys keep movin', Kiryu-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "349||||4"
msgid "Yer fight's with us, y'bastards!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "350||||4"
msgid "Let's go while we still can, Kiryu-aniki!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "352||||4"
msgid "We're done here.\r\nLet's keep pushin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "353||||4"
msgid "Die!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "356||||4"
msgid "Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "357||||4"
msgid "Yuta-kun! Shit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "358||||4"
msgid "That's one down.\r\nWho's next?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "360||||4"
msgid "Shit... Y'asshole!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "361||||4"
msgid "Stay there, Yuta!\r\nDon't move."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "362||||4"
msgid "Hang in there.\r\nThis won't take long."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "363||||4"
msgid "Yuta-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "364||||4"
msgid "Don't give up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "365||||4"
msgid "I-It's okay.\r\nThis is nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "366||||4"
msgid "It definitely <font_kind=yakuza_italic>looks</font_kind> like something.\r\nStay still."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "367||||4"
msgid "We've got important shit to do.\r\nI can't jus'... lie here like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "368||||4"
msgid "Akiyama. Can I leave Yuta to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "369||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "370||||4"
msgid "I said stay still!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "371||||4"
msgid "Goddammit...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "372||||4"
msgid "Yuta!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "374||||4"
msgid "If you die on me here, I'd never be able\r\nto face Haruka and Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "375||||4"
msgid "You need to live.\r\nLive, and protect your family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "376||||4"
msgid "Aniki..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "378||||4"
msgid "Akiyama. He's yours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "379||||4"
msgid "Be careful up there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "381||||4"
msgid "Who is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "382||||4"
msgid "The one you seek, Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "383||||4"
msgid "Sugai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "384||||4"
msgid "I expected you to come here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "385||||4"
msgid "However, I don't have time to play with you today.\r\nI've delegated that to someone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "386||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "387||||4"
msgid "Where are you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "388||||4"
msgid "It doesn't matter now where I am!\r\nKiryu..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "389||||4"
msgid "This is where you die.\r\nI look forward to watching it happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "390||||4"
msgid "So Sugai and his lackeys took Kiyomi-san\r\nhostage, then killed her right in front of Someya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "391||||4"
msgid "No... Kiyomi-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "392||||4"
msgid "They'll pay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "393||||4"
msgid "We really gonna take this lyin' down?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "394||||4"
msgid "I know. But we'll have time to talk later.\r\nWe can't stay here anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "395||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "396||||4"
msgid "They'll come for us next."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "397||||4"
msgid "They won't stop until they get revenge\r\nfor revealing the secret of Onomichi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "398||||4"
msgid "It's dangerous to be all in the same place like this.\r\nWe need to hide separately for a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "400||||4"
msgid "You're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "401||||4"
msgid "If only we knew where Iwami and Sugai were.\r\nWe'd have a better chance if we did."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "402||||4"
msgid "Cap?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "403||||4"
msgid "I'm goin' t'get some fresh air on the roof."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "404||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki's right, y'know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "405||||4"
msgid "By the time I come back down here,\r\ny'all better be gone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "406||||4"
msgid "Once things're calmer,\r\nwe can meet up again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "407||||4"
msgid "Don't y'get it!? This ain't the time\r\nt'be sittin' on our asses!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "408||||4"
msgid "Get the fuck outta here!\r\nI ain't lettin' them kill anyone else, y'hear me!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "409||||4"
msgid "Akiyama. Can you take care of Yuta for me? You should be\r\nsafe from both the Tojo and the Yomei down in that sewer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "410||||4"
msgid "Will do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "411||||4"
msgid "How is Haruka doing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "412||||4"
msgid "Date-san's got a handle on it. He'll probably\r\nhave her outta the hospital by sundown."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "413||||4"
msgid "Good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "414||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "415||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "416||||4"
msgid "If yer still hung up about Kiyomi-san...\r\nYou need to know it's not your fault."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "418||||4"
msgid "Once I'm healed,\r\nwe're getting revenge."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "419||||4"
msgid "Mind if I ask you something, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "420||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "421||||4"
msgid "If Sugai really had been up in the Millennium Tower,\r\nwhat do you think you would've done?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "423||||4"
msgid "I keep thinking about it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "424||||4"
msgid "I mean, he and Iwami are ready to do\r\nwhatever it takes to kill you guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "425||||4"
msgid "Plus they have no qualms about hurting\r\nyour friends if it means getting to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "426||||4"
msgid "And they aren't listening to reason."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "427||||4"
msgid "So, there's only one conclusion, Kiryu-san.\r\nWhen you saw Sugai and Iwami..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "428||||4"
msgid "...You were going to kill them, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "429||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "430||||4"
msgid "Am I wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "432||||4"
msgid "But if the Dragon of Dojima gets blood on his hands,\r\nyou'd be finished as the boss of Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "433||||4"
msgid "Don't you put me on a pedestal."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "434||||4"
msgid "I can't protect my own friends, let alone\r\nthe whole city. I'm just a washed-up yakuza."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "435||||4"
msgid "You can say that all you want,\r\nbut I'm not giving up on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "436||||4"
msgid "If Kamurocho falls to the likes of Iwami\r\nand Sugai, there'll be no turning back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "437||||4"
msgid "Right now, this city needs you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "438||||4"
msgid "Think of your legacy. Think of the history\r\nyou've etched into the streets of the city."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "440||||4"
msgid "Look at me. Kamurocho picked me back\r\nup when I was at rock bottom."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "441||||4"
msgid "If you're planning to get your hands dirty,\r\nI'd rather you use mine instead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "443||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-aniki. The others bail yet?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "444||||4"
msgid "They're gone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "446||||4"
msgid "You had something to say to me, Nagumo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "447||||4"
msgid "Tsuneo Iwami's gonna head t'the shipyard\r\ntomorrow fer Takeru Kurusu's funeral."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "448||||4"
msgid "You're sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "449||||4"
msgid "They're callin' it a Yomei succession ceremony.\r\nThey'll be comin' from across Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "450||||4"
msgid "Ino looked into it fer me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "451||||4"
msgid "I heard Sugai's gonna be there, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "453||||4"
msgid "Y'know, I'll do whatever it takes t'see\r\nthem dead. Ya with me on that, Aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "454||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "455||||4"
msgid "It's gotta be jus' the two of us, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "456||||4"
msgid "We can't let anyone else get involved.\r\nNot the rest o' the family, n' not Akiyama-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "457||||4"
msgid "I was thinking the same."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "458||||4"
msgid "When we die, at least we'll go\r\ntogether... As brothers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "459||||4"
msgid "Probly the first bit o' good news\r\nI've heard all day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "461||||4"
msgid "I'm ready t'get goin' whenever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "462||||4"
msgid "I know yer probly not ready yet, Aniki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "463||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "464||||4"
msgid "Take yer time sayin' goodbye t'Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "465||||4"
msgid "I'll be waitin' fer ya in Serena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "466||||4"
msgid "Lemme know once y'finish all yer business.\r\nLater."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "467||||4"
msgid "(This is my final night in Kamurocho.\r\nWhatever's ahead, I need to be ready.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "468||||4"
msgid "Aniki. Yer done doin' what y'needed\r\nt'do in Kamurocho, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "469||||4"
msgid "If y'are, we can finally go put all this t'bed.\r\nSo how 'bout it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "470||||4"
msgid "No, I'm not ready yet.\r\nGive me a little more time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "471||||4"
msgid "All right, let's do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "472||||4"
msgid "Somethin' wrong?\r\nI ain't done with ya yet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "474||||4"
msgid "C'mon!\r\nThat ain't enough t'stop me!"
msgstr ""

